BEGIN:VEVENT
X-SOURCE:IU Media School
DTSTART:20260612T223000Z
DTEND:20260612T233000Z
LOCATION:Buskirk-Chumley Theater
GEO:39.166284;-86.532809
SUMMARY:Godzilla Weekend: Mothra Madness - Mothra (1961)
DESCRIPTION:Join us at the theater for a mayoral proclamation video and a
  post-film discussion featuring a film scholar and organizer of the Bloom
 ington International Film Festival Matt Rice. The event also includes mer
 chandise from Badknees\, a live performance by Madam McVillian\, and appe
 arances by artist Matt Frank.
X-ALT-DESC;FMTTYPE=text/html:<p>  Join us at the theater for a mayoral pr
 oclamation video and a post-film discussion featuring a film scholar and 
 organizer of the Bloomington International Film Festival Matt Rice. The e
 vent also includes merchandise from Badknees\, a live performance by Mada
 m McVillian\, and appearances by artist Matt Frank.</p>
UID:20260612T223000Z-2270699@events.iu.edu
DTSTAMP:20260416T115618Z
URL:https://events.iu.edu/mediaiub/event/2270699-godzilla-weekend-mothra-
 madness-mothra-1961
CATEGORIES:Performances, shows, and films
LAST-MODIFIED:20260416T155618Z
ATTACH:https://events.iu.edu/live/image/gid/45/width/168/height/168/crop/
 1/src_region/0,0,238,238/30944_061226_Mothra_Flyer.rev.1776354965.png
X-LIVEWHALE-TYPE:events
X-LIVEWHALE-ID:2270699
X-LIVEWHALE-TIMEZONE:America/New_York
X-LIVEWHALE-IMAGE:https://events.iu.edu/live/image/gid/45/width/168/heigh
 t/168/crop/1/src_region/0\,0\,238\,238/30944_061226_Mothra_Flyer.rev.1776
 354965.png
X-LIVEWHALE-COST:17.00
X-LIVEWHALE-CONTACT-INFO:<p>Questions? Contact BCT: <a href="mailto:boxof
 fice@buskirkchumley.org">boxoffice@buskirkchumley.org</a>&#160\;</p>
X-LIVEWHALE-SUMMARY:<p>This is the first night for the Godzilla Weekend\,
  where the first film featuring Mothra will be screened and praised.</p>
END:VEVENT
