X-SOURCE:IU Media School
DTSTART:20260613T153000Z
DTEND:20260613T221500Z
LOCATION:Buskirk-Chumley Theater
GEO:39.166284;-86.532809
SUMMARY:Godzilla weekend: Mothra Madness Film Fest
DESCRIPTION:Spanning multiple eras of kaiju cinema\, these films blend ep
 ic battles\, environmental themes\, and shifting moral roles between dest
 ruction and guardianship.
